I tried option 3 above.  agl pointed out that ViewHostMsg_AllocTransportDIB can be used to create a shared memory segment on Mac.  However, this is not available in the sel_ldr process.  While we use RenderThread::current() for NaCl in render_process_impl.cc, this returns NULL in nacl_thread.cc.

In the end I have gone with option 2 above.</ns0:content><ns0:updated>2010-11-11T15:09:36.000Z</ns0:updated><ns0:published>2010-11-11T15:09:36.000Z</ns0:published><ns2:updates>
